<br>
I'm not positive, but I think slaughter for the Islamic law of halal may be exactly the same as for kosher.  We had an Arab Muslim visit us on the Jewish Families board at BC and she said that where she lives she purchases kosher products in order to follow halal rules.  Where is our resident Muslim?  Kate?  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
